                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <b>
                                Pain:
                            </b>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            This is a common symptom in neurological disorders, and it can be easy to overlook it. However, as you keep ignoring the pain, it will get more intense and unbearable.
                            The chronic pain can be related to age as well, so its best that you dont overlook this sign and get it checked.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Experiencing trouble with memory:
                        </p>
                        <p>
